title: Kylie Jenner married to Tyga at 17? Shows off new diamond ring on Instagram | The
text:
SHE’S just 17, but Kylie Jenner has sparked marriage rumours after sporting a new diamond band on her left ring finger.
The reality TV star shared two glam Instagram selfies flaunting her new jewellery (one focusing on her new bling), adding fuel to speculation she has wed her 25-year-old rapper boyfriend, Tyga.
Has Kylie Jenner tied the knot? (Frame content direct link: https://instagram.com/p/5qWK4iHGi3/embed .)
In the photos, she wears two rings on her wedding finger.
She began wearing the first ring in May, sparking engagement rumours.
Now she’s wearing a new band which appears to be encrusted with diamonds.
'Looking over at little Kylie like...' (Frame content direct link: https://instagram.com/p/5qZzrjHGpn/embed .)
But it’s not just the new bling causing a stir.
The Keeping Up With The Kardashians star seemed to hint at a secret wedding during the premiere episode of I Am Cait , a TV documentary about Bruce Jenner’s transition to Caitlyn Jenner.
Kylie Jenner in 'I Am Cait' (Frame content direct link: https://www.youtube.com/embed/bDuq3b10YfU .)
On Sunday night, Caitlyn Jenner’s mum Esther gave her granddaughter a photo of her when she was 17.
“I thought you should have this. It’s me when I was 17,” the 89-year-old matriarch said.
“Oh my God. Wait, we kind of look alike,” the young Jenner replied. “I definitely take the Jenner side.”
Caitlyn Jenner, 65, chimed in: “Here’s the kicker, she was 17 years old in this picture and she was married.”
Kylie Jenner then dropped the bombshell: “Kind of like me.”
“I’d better not hear that from you,” the former Olympian responded.
Newlyweds? ... Kylie Jenner and Tyga are rumoured to have tied the knot. Picture: Lilly Lawrence/WireImage Source: New York Post
Hollywood Life reports Tyga and Kylie Jenner are expected to make their nuptials official after the young model turns 18 in August.
Tyga, real name Michael Ray Nguyen-Stevenson, has a son, King Cairo Stevenson, with former stripper, Blac Chyna.
Originally published as Has Kylie Jenner tied the knot?
